## 7. Optional integrations

Uncomment and fill in the relevant section in `docker-compose.yml`:

- **OpenAI-compatible API server** — set `API_SERVER_HOST` + `API_SERVER_KEY`
  (key is mandatory). See `docs/user-guide/api-server.md`.
- **Microsoft Teams** — register a bot at `dev.botframework.com`, set
  `TEAMS_CLIENT_ID`, `TEAMS_CLIENT_SECRET`, `TEAMS_TENANT_ID`,
  `TEAMS_ALLOWED_USERS`, optionally `TEAMS_PORT`.
- **Google Chat** — set `GOOGLE_CHAT_PROJECT_ID`,
  `GOOGLE_CHAT_SUBSCRIPTION_NAME`, `GOOGLE_CHAT_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON`
  (must be a mount path), `GOOGLE_CHAT_ALLOWED_USERS`. Add a volume entry
  for the SA JSON file.

